signature: Observable<Entry<T, S>> search(Func1<? super Geometry, Boolean> condition)

enhanced_by.reason: Environment setup is required before performing searches on the R-tree.
Entries must be added to the R-tree before they can be searched.
The search results should be verified to ensure they match the expected entries based on the condition.
The depth of the R-tree can be used to verify the complexity of the search operation.
